last_episode_to_air.name: Ingoku Byoutou
last_episode_to_air.overview: Jyunichi, a famous hospital doctor in Japan, wants to take over Misono Hospital as Managing Director. But then the son of the Hospital Director then appeared he was Serika. Having returned from his studies as a doctor, Jyunichi who knew this immediately made an evil plan to expel Serika and take over the Hospital.
